},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, L, Msb:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafaAfiyHu","text_ar":"تَفَافِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) and the dim. of the n. un. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tufayofyHapN","text_ar":"تُفَيْفيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN tuHofatuhu tuf~aAHapN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ تُحْفَتُهُ تُفَّاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one, his present is an apple"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuf~aAHu AlHub~i","text_ar":"تُفَّاحُ الحُبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuf~aAHN *ahabiY~N","text_ar":"تُفَّاحٌ ذَهَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baA*anojaAnN","text_ar":"بَاذَنْجَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuf~aAHu","text_ar":"تُفَّاحُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albar~i","text_ar":"البَرِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaboruwHN","text_ar":"يَبْرُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brH","text_ar":"برح"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~uf~aAHapu","text_ar":"التُّفَّاحَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The head of the thigh-bone, which is in the haunch-bone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, A, K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laTamona biAlEun~aAbi Alt~uf~aAHa","text_ar":"لَطَمْنَ بِالعُنَّابِ التُّفَّاحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They"},{"kind":"text","text":"(women)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slapped, with the jujubes, the apples"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the fingers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the ends of the fingers, the cheeks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"}],"source_refs":["L","Msb",